OL,7,FNicolas Sarkozy has been found guilty
OL,8,Fof criminal conspiracy in a case
OL,9,Flinked to the late Libyan dictator
OL,10,FMuammar Gaddafi's government.
OL,12,FThe former French President was
OL,13,Faccused of financing his presidential
OL,14,Fcampaign with millions of euros from
OL,15,FLibya in exchange for diplomatic
OL,16,Ffavours between 2005 and 2007.
