OL,5,Cregime
OL,7,FThe 70-year-old was acquitted of three
OL,8,Fother charges: passive corruption,
OL,9,Fillegal campaign financing and
OL,10,Fconcealment of the embezzlement of
OL,11,Fpublic funds.
OL,13,FThe accusations go back to 2011, when
OL,14,Fa Libyan news agency and Gaddafi
OL,15,Fhimself said the Libyan state had
OL,16,Fsecretly funnelled millions of euros
OL,17,Finto Sarkozy's 2007 campaign.
