OL,7,FThe sentencing will come later in
OL,8,Fcourt proceedings, and the court is
OL,9,Fstill detailing its ruling, but
OL,10,Fcriminal association is a serious
OL,11,Fcharge that carries a potential
OL,12,Fsentence of up to ten years in prison.
OL,14,FSarkozy will be able to appeal the
OL,15,Fguilty verdict.
