OL,7,FOverall, the verdicts appeared to
OL,8,Fsuggest that the court believed that
OL,9,Fthe men conspired together to seek
OL,10,FLibyan funding for Sarkozy's 2007
OL,11,Fcampaign but that judges weren't
OL,12,Fconvinced that the conservative leader
OL,13,Fhimself was guilty of putting the
OL,14,Fscheme in place.
OL,16,FSarkozy was present in the courtroom,
OL,17,Faccompanied by his wife, the singer
OL,18,Fand model Carla Bruni-Sarkozy, as well
OL,19,Fas his three adult sons.
