OL,7,FHe was elected in 2007 but lost his
OL,8,Fbid for reelection in 2012. He denied
OL,9,Fall wrongdoing during a three-month
OL,10,Ftrial earlier this year that also
OL,11,Finvolved 11 co-defendants, including
OL,12,Fthree former ministers.
OL,14,FDespite multiple legal scandals that
OL,15,Fhave clouded his presidential legacy,
OL,16,FSarkozy remains an influential figure
OL,17,Fin right-wing politics in France and
OL,18,Fin entertainment circle.
